
Suddenly, girls started roaming around Roby that was sitting beside me.
"Mr.Clows, how are you?" One girl said.
"Mr.Clows, will you please accept these chocolates, they are homemade." Another said.
"Tsk. Tsk. Tsk." A shook my head in disapproval. Roby flushed. He was angry and I sealed my lips so I don't burst from laughter.
Surprisingly, Dr.Ali was our teacher. He started our first lesson about differences between the human body and the vampire body.
And it was boring!
